  <h1>Live Search</h1>

  <div class="block">
    <h2>Searches in AmiGO</h2>
    
    <p>
      Live Search will return results from the Gene Ontology as you
      type. No results will be returned until the search input is at
      least three characters. After that, you may also use the filters
      to limit or reduce the results.
    </p>
      
    <p>
      For a detailed explanation on how to search, a list of what
      fields can be used in the search string, or an explanation for
      how to get the results you want, please view the AmiGO
      <a title="Go to Live Search documentation"
	 href="http://wiki.geneontology.org/index.php/AmiGO_Manual:_Live_Search">Live Search documentation</a>.
    </p>

